1. Write a C++ Program to display Names, Roll No., and grades of 3 students who have appeared in the examination. Declare the class of name, Roll No., and grade. 
Create an array of class objects. Read and display the contents of the array. 
i) without using any functions
ii) using functions for getting and printing data

2. Write a C++ program to declare Struct. Initialize and display contents of member Variables. 
i) without using any functions
ii) using functions for getting and printing data

3. Write a C++ program to declare a class. Declare a pointer to the class. Initialize and display the contents of the class member. 

4. Given that an EMPLOYEE class contains the following members: data members: Employee number, Employee name, Basic, DA, IT, Net Salary and print data members 

5. . Write a C++ program to read the data of N employee and compute Net salary of each employee (DA=52% of Basic and Income Tax (IT) =30% of the gross salary).
